## 12 February 2026 (Weekend Mini Project)

### Project: Simple Interactive Page

### Features

* Button click par text change
* Basic DOM + Event handling

### Code

```html id="js08"
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<p id="demo">Click the button</p>

<button onclick="changeText()">Click Me</button>

<script>
function changeText() {
    document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "Text Changed";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
```

